# Python / uv per-folder isolation
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc

# Local CLAUDE.md (recursive, per ~/CLAUDE.md rule). The top-level
# CLAUDE.md is the EXCEPTION — it documents the reproduction
# methodology and IS tracked.
**/CLAUDE.md
!CLAUDE.md

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Quarto build outputs
**/_files/
**/_freeze/
**/_book/
**/*.quarto_ipynb
.quarto/
